 how do we denote that? Well, they're not equal.

24
00:01:09,485 --> 00:01:10,840
 The two numbers are not equal,

25
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,670
 but they're congruent in this,

26
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:15,715
 or they're equivalent in this world modular N.

27
